    {
      "text": "Shining Force: The Sword of Hajya is a 1993 tactical role-playing game developed by Sonic! Software Planning and published by Sega for the Game Gear.\nIt is not to be confused with Shining Force II, as this Gaiden II is the sequel to the original Shining Force Gaiden. Along with the original Gaiden, The Sword of Hajya was remade as Shining Force CD, which contains two new scenarios that further continue the story of Cypress.",
